Description: Flight into Egypt, with Virgin holding Child and standing at the end of a footbridge; on the left St Joseph leading the donkey on the footbridge; on the right, a ferryman standing in his boat and leaning on the oar; classical buildings on a hillside in the background, at left; counterproof Etching
